           if        rf-zst-tip-cls       not  = 01
                     go to det-zon-dcc-600.
           if        rf-zst-des-key       not  = rf-gxp-des-upp
                     go to det-zon-dcc-600.
       det-zon-dcc-540.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
