           move      rf-zst-cod-cls       to   w-det-zon-dcc-cod      .
           add       1                    to   w-det-zon-dcc-cod      .
       det-zon-dcc-600.
           if        w-det-zon-dcc-cod    >    zero
                     go to det-zon-dcc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
