      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-gxc-cod-cmn       to   w-det-cap-cfl-cmn      .
           move      rf-gxc-cod-fzn       to   w-det-cap-cfl-fzn      .
           move      rf-gxc-cod-lct       to   w-det-cap-cfl-lct      .
